VALUES
  ('mem_i001','1.0','ws_spec0001','使用者認證：Email 與密碼','User authentication: email and password','procedural','plain',
   'MemTrace 採用 Email + Password 認證路徑。安全措施包括：bcrypt 雜湊（cost ≥ 12）、密碼政策（8–128 字元、大小寫+數字、HaveIBeenPwned 洩漏檢查）、email 驗證信（24 小時效期）、失敗 5 次鎖定 15 分鐘。登入後核發 JWT Session（7 天），透過 Authorization: Bearer 標頭傳遞，登出以 blocklist 立即失效。目前不支援第三方 OAuth 登入，以簡化認證表面並減少外部依賴。','MemTrace uses Email + Password authentication. Security measures include: bcrypt hash (cost ≥ 12), password policy (8–128 chars, upper+lower+digit, HaveIBeenPwned check), verification email (24h expiry), and 5-failure lockout for 15 minutes. Upon login, a JWT session (7 days) is issued and passed via the Authorization: Bearer header. Logout is handled via an immediate blocklist. Third-party OAuth is currently not supported to simplify the authentication surface and reduce external dependencies.',ARRAY['auth', 'security', 'jwt', 'password-policy']::text[],'public',
   'memtrace-spec','2026-04-11T00:00:00Z','a4b5c6d7e8f9a4b5c6d7e8f9a4b5c6d7e8f9a4b5c6d7e8f9a4b5c6d7e8f9a4b5','human',
   0.95,0.95,1.0,0.9,0.9,
   0,0,0,0,0)
ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
  title_zh=EXCLUDED.title_zh, title_en=EXCLUDED.title_en,
